Constructor

Parameters:
isPublic - whether generated class and its methods will have 'public' access modifier
useIterableJdbcTemplate - whether to use iterable jdbc template extensions from this project (https://github.com/alexkasko/springjdbc-iterable)
useCheckSingleRowUpdates - whether to generate additional update methods, those check that only single row was changed on update
useBatchInserts - whether to generate additional insert (DML) methods (with parameters), those takes Iterator of parameters and execute inserts for the contents of the specified iterator in batch mode
useTemplateStringSubstitution - whether to recognize query templates on method generation
selectRegex - regular expression to use for identifying 'select' queries by name
updateRegex - regular expression to use for identifying 'insert', 'update' and 'delete' queries by name
templateRegex - regular expression to recognize query templates by name
templateValueConstraintRegex - regular expression constraint for template substitution values
typeIdMap - mapping of parameter names postfixes to data types
freemarkerTemplate - freemarker template body
freemarkerConf - freemarker configuration @throws CodeGeneratorException on any error
